{
  "stem": "4289.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I insisted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, Ester, you must study.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't care if you know how to cook, how to clean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You have to study.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was her whole effort and my effort.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What she studied was my dream probably.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she did finish school with honors and got right away a very good position.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ester is very bright and smart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I take advice from my daughter now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She has two children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have two grandchildren, which is a miracle of itself that our family is getting larger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when Ester married and she moved out, not far, thank goodness, I felt really alone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was thinking about my sister and my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Wouldn't it be nice, you know, for holidays, I could invite them, could have other people here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I heard people have cousins club, I said, God, what a wonderful idea!",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But where am I going to get all the cousins from?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I felt, always like there was something missing in my life, like a hand or leg, or-- And I was thinking about this brother of mine, that my father told me that I had a twin brother, and older sister, Genia.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Poland, one of my aunt's daughter, Basia, the one who is in Brazil, she hid one of the pictures of our family that she had in the attic.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the war she came there, and she found it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a picture of my sister, and my father, and my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I still didn't have the picture of Adam, my twin brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came to United States, we had some family that lived here long before the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
